: 34px; align-items: center;\">[15]Understanding Critical Discourse Analysis in Qualitative Research. https:///www.arcjournals.org&gt;ijhsse</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[16]https:///www.slideshare.net (2015). The Role of Context (Discourse Analysis)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[17]https://en.wikipedia.org. Who Coined the Term Discourse?</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[18]https:///www.brigthubeducation.com. Discourse Theory on Second Language Acquisition.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[19]https://koppa.jyu.fi</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[20]https://education.stateuniversity.com. What does discourse mean in Education?</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[21]https://www.thoughco.com. What is the Concept of Discourse?</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[22]https://www.linguisticsociety.org.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px