(169, '<div><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: capitalize;\">The Gospel Of John Contains Several Individual Conversations.The Conversations Included Nicodemus, A Samaritan Woman, And A Man Born Blind. To Interpret The Content Of The Conversations, The Author Uses A Heuristic Reasoning Approach; The Findings Of The Study Show The Benefits And Depth Of Heuristic Reasoning, Especially The Content Of The Conversation And Its Application In Christian Education Services.</span><br></div>', '<div><ul class=\"reference-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[1]Adrian and Christopher (2014), “Heuristic and Analytical Processes in Reasoning: An Event-Related Potential Study of Belief Bias”. Psychology.51</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[2]Álvaro Ferreira Rodrigues, Nuno (2015) Heuristics In Problem-Solving For The Teaching And Learning Of Mathematics. Dissertation. Faculty of Psychology and Educat