px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[11]Waters, K., Altiparmak, S. O., Shutters, S. T., &amp; Thies, C. (2024). The Green Mirage: The EU’s Complex Relationship with Palm Oil Biodiesel in the Context of Environmental Narratives and Global Trade Dynamics. Energies, 17(2), 343.</li></ul></div>', '', '[{\"firstname\":\"Ros\",\"middlename\":\"Tamaji\",\"lastname\":\"Korniawan\",\"affiliation\":[\"University Of Indonesia: Universitas\"],\"email\":\"ostamaji_k@yahoo.com\",\"orchid_id\":null}]', '[{\"name\":\"University Of Indonesia: Universitas\",\"country\":\"Indonesia\"}]', 47, '2024-06-26 14:30:21', '2024-06-26 14:30:21'),
(176, '<div><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: capitalize;\">Fiberglass Ferrocement Roof Reinforced Is Considered To Be A Sustainable, Enduring, And Cost-Effective Roofing Solution. Improved Mechanical Qualities, A Wide Variety Of Uses, Environmental Resilience, And Sustainability Make It A Competitive Choice For Many Building Endeavors. Fiberglass Ferrocement Roof Reinforced Has The Potential To Become An Industry-Standard Roofing Material By Overcoming Current Obstacles And Expanding Into New Areas. The Full Potential Of Fiberglass Ferrocement Roof Reinforced And The Advancement Of The Field Of Building Materials And Technologies Depend On Ongoing Research, Innovation, And Cooperation. The Results Of This Study Deliver The Basis For Further Investigation And Policymaking, Propelling The Widespread Use Of This Cutting-Edge Roofing Material To Create A More Sustainable And Resilient Built Environment.</span><br></div>', '<div><ul class=\"reference-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Liberation Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 12px 2px; scrollbar-width: auto; scrollbar-color: rgb(57, 110, 181) rgb(255, 255, 255); display: flex; gap: 30px; border-radius: 34px; align-items: center;\">[1]Al-Asadi, M. J., Salman, T. I., Al-Bayati, A. R., &amp; Ghos