(6, 'Future of Learning: Educational Innovation through Technology', 'future-of-learning-educational-innovation-through-technology', NULL, '[{\"value\":\"Blended Learning\"},{\"value\":\"Higher Education\"},{\"value\":\"Learning Outcomes\"}]', 'case study', '<div><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Educational innovation fueled by\r\ntechnology has revolutionized teaching and learning methodologies, offering\r\ntransformative opportunities to enhance student engagement, personalized\r\nlearning experiences, and prepare learners for a rapidly evolving global landscape.\r\nAt Guinness Press, we delve into the dynamic intersection of educational\r\ninnovation and technology through a compelling case study that highlights\r\nsuccessful implementations, benefits, and implications for future educational\r\npractices.<br><br><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Case\r\nStudy: Implementing Blended Learning in Higher Education<br><br><o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n<div><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Background<br><o:p></o:p></span></b></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">This case study examines the adoption\r\nof blended learning in