fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n     mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Enhanced retention and\r\n     understanding of complex concepts.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n     mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Development of critical thinking\r\n     and problem-solving skills.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">Example:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-ligatures:none\"> Duolingo, a language-learning app, uses gamification to\r\nencourage users to practice regularly, offering points, levels, and badges to\r\nkeep learners motivated.<o:p></o:p></span></div><div><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\r\nmso-ligatures:none\"><br></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ligatures:none\">4. Virtual and Augmented Reality\r\n(VR/AR):</span></b><span styl